<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="due-to">due to</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>由于；因为：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The town was cut off from the rest of the world due to heavy snow.
由于暴雪，这个小镇与外界隔绝了。</p><footer>2016 北京</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The water shortage is severe mainly due to global warming, environmental pollution and the everincreasing population.
水资源严重短缺主要是由全球变暖、环境污染和人口持续增长造成的。</p><footer>2010 福建书面表达改</footer></div></div>